column5: Man catches muskie with his bare... foot  Someone asked me if I was related to this guy, on account of the matching last name and love for fishing.   (Sorry if this was already posted - I looked and didn't see it, thought some of you might get a kick out of it).
Noodling for musky -- now that's a real man's sport!
Ouuchh , I guess he doesnt understand the meaning of live bait LOL
now i bet that guys happy MUSKIES believe in live release
Dang..........All that musky gear i bought ..............useless
So he says 8kg's but the female newscaster calls it 40 pounds? I like her. Any woman that can give a guy that much credit is ok in my books
Was he wearing firetiger toenail polish
Good story thanks Dana.  They could use the feet that they found in TO to fish with.

hahaha, I seen this on Gussy Twitter during the tourny.  Guess whos gonna think twice about fishing in sandals?  I bet that was sore the next day, but man, whatta good story to pass on later in life. I'd be thankful it happened the way it did, doods got a man card for life now, no matter what else goes on!
